        <div class="tab-pane fade" id="tab-posting">
           <div class="alert alert-info border-info shadow-sm mb-3 d-none" id="noChargePostingNotice">
              <div class="fw-bold mb-1"><i class="bi bi-info-circle me-2"></i>No-Charge Class</div>
              <div class="small text-muted">
                 Posting Policies are not required for No-Charge classes. Class-level transaction generation is skipped.
                 Switch Billing Mode to <strong>Chargeable Class</strong> if you want class fees posted.
