           </div>
           <div class="alert alert-warning border-warning shadow-sm mb-3">
              <div class="fw-bold mb-1"><i class="bi bi-cash-stack me-2"></i>Class Fee Posting Policies</div>
              <div class="small text-muted">
                 Fee amounts are defined in the <strong>Pricing</strong> tab. This tab only assigns the Posting Policy for each fee category.
                 Use a Transaction Template with posting entries set to <strong>Amount 0</strong>. Then the runtime class fee amount for the student's fee category will be posted through that template and split by row percentage.
